sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Web as Blazor Web
    participant Auth as API Auth
    participant API
    User->>Web: Credenciales
    Web->>Auth: POST /login
    Auth-->>Web: JWT
    Web->>API: Authorization: Bearer JWT
    API->>API: Validar firma, issuer, audience y claims
    API-->>Web: Recurso autorizado
